BREAKING: Department of Health confirms 943 more COVID-19 cases -- 578 detected in past three days, 365 part of validation backlog. 

Total infections rise to 29,400, with 7,650 recoveries and 1,150 deaths. https://t.co/msCLmwV0u6 https://t.co/t8v6kWa6AO
